{
  "stem": "23641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We almost died there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we decided, we cannot stay longer here, because we're going to die there anyways for hunger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because before us was other people coming in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the girls used to tell us-- well, they used to take care in the houses, clean the houses there-- that every time, they bring in new people there, and-- and they never go home.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They always die out there-- always die out there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We decided we were-- we were-- six boys, what they let us go from the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all wound up in Arkhangelsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We decided that we have to go away from there-- that's going to be the end of us there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, I was already weak, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I just couldn't walk too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one-- one evening, we went on the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we decided to go back, because being in Arkhangelsk, I heard on the radio announcing, that my city, Wlodawa, was already taken over by the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I wanted to go back to Wlodawa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When was this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Summer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, summer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so-- we were traveling all night long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when we came from Arkhangelsk, we had to go to-- we took the route to Vologda.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we were sitting in the-- in the toilet there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we thought, nobody's going to bother us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we came near Vologda, somebody opens up the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, hey, [NON-ENGLISH], what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, comrades, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us off, and they took us to Vologda.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while we were going down, I think four guys disappeared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I with another one-- they kept us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other four, we don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
